'''喬瑟夫·派翠克·溫德爾'''（{{lang-en|'''Joseph Patrick Wendle'''}}，{{bd|1990年|4月26日|}}），為[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的二壘手，目前效力於邁阿密馬林魚。他先前曾效力過運動家與光芒等隊。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
溫德爾出生於[[特拉華州|特拉華州]][[威爾明頓_(特拉華州)|威明頓]]，就讀於賓州Avon Grove高中、{{link-en|西切斯特大學|West Chester University}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2012/04/18/wcus-wendle-one-of-areas-best/ |title=WCU's Wendle One of Area's Best – CBS Philly |publisher=Philadelphia.cbslocal.com |date=2012-04-18 |access-date=2019-04-01 |archive-date=2019-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401081831/https://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2012/04/18/wcus-wendle-one-of-areas-best/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 職業生涯 ===
==== 克里夫蘭印地安人 ====
[[2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，溫德爾在第6輪被印地安人選走<ref>{{cite web |url=http://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2012/06/07/west-chesters-wendle-follows-up-title-with-draft/ |title=West Chester’s Wendle Follows Up Title With Draft |publisher=CBS Philadelphia |date=2012-06-07 |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712131118/https://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2012/06/07/west-chesters-wendle-follows-up-title-with-draft/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://wcupagoldenrams.com/news/2012/6/5/BB_0605121205.aspx |title=oe Wendle Selected In Sixth Round By Cleveland Indians |publisher=Wcupagoldenrams.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2020-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715175248/https://wcupagoldenrams.com/news/2012/6/5/BB_0605121205.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他從短期1A開啟他的職棒生涯<ref>{{cite web |url=http://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2012/08/23/west-chesters-wendle-just-keeps-on-hitting/ |title=West Chester’s Wendle Just Keeps On Hitting |publisher=CBS Philadelphia |date=2012-08-23 |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123071305/https://philadelphia.cbslocal.com/2012/08/23/west-chesters-wendle-just-keeps-on-hitting/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年，他升上高階1A<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.news-herald.com/general-news/20130717/indians-carolina-second-baseman-joe-wendle-could-be-hidden-gem-in-tribes-farm-system |title=Indians: Carolina second baseman Joe Wendle could be hidden gem in Tribe's farm system |work=News-Herald |date= |accessdate=2014-04-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054432/http://www.news-herald.com/general-news/20130717/indians-carolina-second-baseman-joe-wendle-could-be-hidden-gem-in-tribes-farm-system |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在隔年升上2A<ref>{{cite news|last1=Legard|first1=Ron|title=Indians name David Wallace as manager of RubberDucks along with rest of coaching staff|url=http://www.ohio.com/blogs/akron-aeros/rubberducks-1.293028/indians-name-david-wallace-as-manager-of-rubberducks-along-with-rest-of-coaching-staff-1.453992?localLinksEnabled=false|accessdate=2014-12-08|work=Akron Beacon Journal|date=2013-12-20|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924055311/http://www.ohio.com/blogs/akron-aeros/rubberducks-1.293028/indians-name-david-wallace-as-manager-of-rubberducks-along-with-rest-of-coaching-staff-1.453992?localLinksEnabled=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Cahill|first1=Teddy|title=Lindor, Wendle erupt at plate for Double-A Akron|url=http://m.indians.mlb.com/news/article/80342834/francisco-lindor-joe-wendle-erupt-at-plate-in-double-a-akrons-rout|accessdate=2014-12-08|publisher=MLB.com|date=2014-06-17|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051844/http://m.indians.mlb.com/news/article/80342834/francisco-lindor-joe-wendle-erupt-at-plate-in-double-a-akrons-rout|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 奧克蘭運動家 ====
2014年12月8日，印地安人將溫德爾交易至運動家，換來Brandon Moss<ref>{{cite news|title=Indians acquire Brandon Moss|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/11999569/cleveland-indians-acquire-brandon-moss-oakland-athletics-minor-leaguer|accessdate=2014-12-08|agency=Associated Press|publisher=ESPN.com|date=2014-12-08|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306141746/http://espn.go.com/mlb/story/_/id/11999569/cleveland-indians-acquire-brandon-moss-oakland-athletics-minor-leaguer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年4月21日，他在德州遊騎兵3A主場敲出該場地啟用的首轟<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150421&content_id=119716320&fext=.jsp&vkey=recap&sid=t556|title=Sounds Bested By Dodgers In Series Opener|website=MILB.com|date=2015-04-21|accessdate=2015-04-22|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325223844/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150421&content_id=119716320&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&sid=t556|dead-url=no}}</ref>。運動家也在球季結束後將他加進40人名單內<ref>{{cite web |last=Lee |first=Jane |url=http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/157785614/as-add-two-prospects-to-40-man-roster |title=Wendle, Torres added to A's 40-man roster |publisher=M.athletics.mlb.com |date= |accessdate=2019-04-01 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083324/http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/157785614/as-add-two-prospects-to-40-man-roster |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年8月31日，溫德爾登上大聯盟<ref>{{cite web|last=Ray|first=Jordan|url=http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/198734792/athletics-call-up-joey-wendle-for-mlb-debut/|title=Wendle gets callup for Major League debut|website=MLB.com|date=2016-08-31|accessdate=2016-08-31|archive-date=2017-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815101455/http://m.athletics.mlb.com/news/article/198734792/athletics-call-up-joey-wendle-for-mlb-debut/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。合計他只在運動家出賽36場比賽，109個打數敲出29支安打。2017年12月7日，運動家將他放進指定讓渡名單中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/athletics-joey-wendle-designated-for-assignment/|title=Athletics' Joey Wendle: Designated for assignment|work=cbssports.com|date=2017-12-07|accessdate=2017-12-07|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712131315/https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/athletics-joey-wendle-designated-for-assignment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 坦帕灣光芒 ====
2017年12月11日，運動家將溫德爾交易至光芒，換來Jonah Heim<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rays/news/rays-acquire-joey-wendle-in-trade-with-as/c-263275840|title=Rays acquire infielder Wendle in deal with A's|work=MLB.com|date=2017-12-11|accessdate=2017-12-11|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622005009/https://www.mlb.com/rays/news/rays-acquire-joey-wendle-in-trade-with-as/c-263275840|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Adams|first=Steve|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/12/rays-trade-jonah-heim-athletics-joey-wendle.html|title=Athletics Acquire Jonah Heim From Rays|website=mlbtraderumors.com|date=2017-12-19|accessdate=2017-12-19|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114073946/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2017/12/rays-trade-jonah-heim-athletics-joey-wendle.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年，他和Micah Johnson與Daniel Robertson一同競爭二壘手的位置<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.draysbay.com/2018/3/12/17101322/tampa-bay-rays-starting-second-baseman-joey-wendle-micah-johnson-daniel-robertson|title=Tampa Bay Rays Season Preview: The Battle for Second Base|work=DRaysBay|access-date=2018-04-10|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712131012/https://www.draysbay.com/2018/3/12/17101322/tampa-bay-rays-starting-second-baseman-joey-wendle-micah-johnson-daniel-robertson|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最後他在春訓繳出了3成27的打擊率，總教練也讓他和Robertson一同分擔二壘的位子<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.draysbay.com/2018/3/28/17173304/tampa-bay-rays-opening-day-roster-2018-chris-archer-kevin-kiermaier|title=Here’s your 2018 Rays Opening Day Roster|work=DRaysBay|access-date=2018-04-10|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712131014/https://www.draysbay.com/2018/3/28/17173304/tampa-bay-rays-opening-day-roster-2018-chris-archer-kevin-kiermaier|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該年他的打擊率為3成<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2018&month=0&season1=2018&ind=2&team=&rost=&age=&filter=&players=|title=Major League Leaderboards » 2018 » Batters » Dashboard {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball|access-date=2018-10-02|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109035704/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=bat&lg=all&qual=y&type=8&season=2018&month=0&season1=2018&ind=2&team=&rost=&age=&filter=&players=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/stats/sortable_rookie.jsp|title=Major League Baseball Rookie Stats|website=Major League Baseball|language=en|access-date=2018-10-02|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107223755/http://mlb.mlb.com/stats/sortable_rookie.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是光芒隊史繼2011年後再次有球員的打擊率可以突破3成<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=380930130|title=Blue Jays vs. Rays - Game Recap - September 30, 2018 - ESPN|website=ESPN.com|language=en|access-date=2018-10-02|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713192143/https://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=380930130|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最後他在美聯新人王票選拿下第四名<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.tampabay.com/blogs/rays/2018/09/28/blake-snell-wins-rays-mvp-award-wendle-smith-also-honored/|title=Blake Snell wins Rays MVP award; Wendle, Smith also honored|date=2018-09-28|access-date=2018-09-28|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109034453/https://www.tampabay.com/blogs/rays/2018/09/28/blake-snell-wins-rays-mvp-award-wendle-smith-also-honored/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/rookie-of-the-year-poll/c-295860692|title=Rookie of the Year poll|website=MLB.com|language=en|access-date=2018-11-21|archive-date=2018-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181212034048/https://www.mlb.com/news/rookie-of-the-year-poll/c-295860692|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年，溫德爾已經站穩了二壘手的位置。不過他在3月31日因為被太空人的[[傑克·馬瑞斯尼克|傑克·馬瑞斯尼克]]滑壘鏟傷腳而進入傷兵名單<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.draysbay.com/2019/4/1/18290747/tampa-bay-rays-to-place-2b-joey-wendle-on-the-injured-list-promote-inf-christian-arroyo|title=Rays place Wendle on IL, promote Arroyo|last=Sanford|first=Adam|date=2019-04-01|website=DRaysBay|access-date=2019-04-01|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401175734/https://www.draysbay.com/2019/4/1/18290747/tampa-bay-rays-to-place-2b-joey-wendle-on-the-injured-list-promote-inf-christian-arroyo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月24日，他又因為被觸身球擊中而再次進傷兵<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rays-lose-another-starter-to-the-injured-list-as-joey-wendle-suffers-fractured-wrist-on-hbp/|title=Rays lose another starter to the injured list as Joey Wendle suffers fractured wrist on HBP|website=CBSSports.com|accessdate=2020-07-12|archive-date=2019-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427173850/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rays-lose-another-starter-to-the-injured-list-as-joey-wendle-suffers-fractured-wrist-on-hbp/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該年他僅出賽75場比賽，打擊率為2成31。在季後賽，溫德爾共出賽5場，擊出2支安打，但球隊未能晉級。

在2020年的縮水賽季，溫德爾出賽50場，儘管一般對他的評價仍是替補選手<ref>{{Cite web|title=He may not be the Rays' MVP, but he's still indispensable|url=https://www.tampabay.com/sports/rays/2020/10/13/he-may-not-be-the-rays-mvp-but-hes-still-indispensable/|access-date=2020-10-14|website=Tampa Bay Times|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017205609/https://www.tampabay.com/sports/rays/2020/10/13/he-may-not-be-the-rays-mvp-but-hes-still-indispensable/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其守備能力的多元性，使他成為二壘、三壘和游擊的主力球員輪休時的替補首選。這年他有著2成86打擊率的成績，光芒則拿下十年來首次分區冠軍。溫德爾在季後賽的表現出色，對陣[[紐約洋基|紐約洋基]]有著3成53的系列賽打擊率，在美聯冠軍系列賽的三壘守備表現更是引人注目。

===邁阿密馬林魚===
2021年球季結束後，光芒隊將溫德爾交易到馬林魚，換來Kameron Misner。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/marlins-trade-for-rays-joey-wendle-as-miami-continues-aggressive-offseason-brinson-designated-for-assignment/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-12-01 |archive-date=2021-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201004900/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/marlins-trade-for-rays-joey-wendle-as-miami-continues-aggressive-offseason-brinson-designated-for-assignment/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 軼事 ==
* 打擊區的溫德爾並不使用打擊手套，而是赤手持棒。這點與前洋基捕手[[賀黑·波薩塔|賀黑·波薩塔]]，以及前光芒球員[[本·佐布里斯特|本·佐布里斯特]]相同。此外，赤手打擊的溫德爾在比賽時仍未取下自己的婚戒，此一特色也引起播報員及球評的注意。

